<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="boast-v">boast <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bəʊst/    美 /boʊst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>夸口 (说)；夸耀 (说)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>boasts that</strong> he is one of the best singers in the country. 
他吹嘘自己是全国最好的歌手之一。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>（地方、机构等）自豪地拥有（好的事物）</strong></h4></div>